The paper is focused on software engineering practices related to continuous integration, delivery, and deployment, which are all subcategories of cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also discusses tools and approaches for implementing these practices, which could fall under cs.SD (Software Development), cs.PL (Programming Languages), or cs.CE (Computational Engineering). Additionally, the paper addresses challenges related to security and reliability, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
